{"tid":1713021,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(請助推，十分重要)(新戰術)如果眾籌買無人機俾前線做哨戒機可行嗎？","createTime":"2019-11-12T16:05:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T13:05:15.000Z","uid":188935,"like":39,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"6cb578605eee5d32e1d70bf478e83a7f3a4fb0a9","tid":1713021,"uid":188935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T16:05:19.000Z","msg":"前排見到有手足用競速無人機喺沙田撚狗，啟發左我諗有冇可能可以各位眾籌課金購買幾十隻無人機俾前線用嚟做偵測用途？買完返嚟，可能組一隊人專門負責做無人機操作員，負責喺後方操作無人機對周邊環境進行偵查，成效應該遠比現行用人肉地面報料嘅方法安全同可靠，而且用依個方法可以喺最快嘅時間內知道狗屋最新動向同佈防。<br />\n<br />\n仲有呢，而家嘅無人機通常都可以cover到幾公里嘅距離，活動範圍大好多。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以好希望依個計劃可以推得成，初步睇下各位有咩睇法，如果反應唔錯可以正式推行籌錢搞"},{"pid":"1cc1a96b098644c7813d63aaed08ede70003645c","tid":1713021,"uid":188935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T16:05:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7179d47315a543d5c1106384afb921ec02c45bd2","tid":1713021,"uid":188935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T16:05:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6f2e1d3b7d28ba957d3fb02bda7a880625122cf4","tid":1713021,"uid":188935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T16:05:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"87d39162678fbe41ae9d01adf29db8c509c92460","tid":1713021,"uid":188935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T16:06:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8aaba226da076925604a012f90cd440f879384a2","tid":1713021,"uid":188935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T16:06:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"93f8f35f427afd2ebb29d65038f2db65e6550fd5","tid":1713021,"uid":53037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T16:06:18.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0be79e55aa04e32360534a2540d1ec6b2df74a8","tid":1713021,"uid":188935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-1